Title: Slime Dies When You're Having Fun
Description:
The investigators here told me that there were some side effects to removing the time anomaly from Eon's Fringe. Seems a bunch of slimes snuck through the timestream in the process. 

Oh! Oh! Time slimes! They're time slimes! Ha.

Anyway, could you take some of them out?
RewardText: I recorded the sounds of you killing the slimes for reference. I hope that's okay.
